cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with dialogue summarization. Additionally, it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves testing several models for automated summarization. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as summarization is a common task in this field. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as neural models are used in the study.
